OL,3,C'Small but positive' rise in retail
OL,4,Cfootfall as sunny April encourages
OL,5,Cshoppers
OL,7,FRetailers have seen a "small but
OL,8,Fpositive" increase in shoppers as the
OL,9,Fsunniest April on record enticed
OL,10,Fconsumers into stores, figures suggest.
OL,12,FFigures for March and April ` which
OL,13,Fcancel out distortions due to this
OL,14,Fyear's late Easter ` indicate high
OL,15,Fstreet footfall increased by 0.2% on
OL,16,Flast year, while visits to retail
OL,17,Fparks were up 2.7%, according to data
OL,18,Ffrom the British Retail Consortium
OL,19,F(BRC) and Sensormatic.
