OL,7,FBut shopping centre visits fell by
OL,8,F0.7%.
OL,10,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,11,Fsaid: "Adjusting for the late fall of
OL,12,FEaster this year, footfall across
OL,13,FMarch and April showed a small but
OL,14,Fpositive trend, with retail parks
OL,15,Fcontinuing to perform the strongest
OL,16,Fout of all locations.
