OL,3,C'Small but positive' rise in retail
OL,4,Cfootfall as sunny April encourages
OL,5,Cshoppers
OL,7,F"This reflected the unseasonally warm
OL,8,Fand bright weather right across the
OL,9,FUK. Retailers will be hoping this
OL,10,Fmomentum continues into the summer
OL,11,Fmonths."
OL,13,FAndy Sumpter, retail consultant for
OL,14,FSensormatic, said: "The combination of
OL,15,FEaster trading and the sunniest April
OL,16,Fon record helped entice consumers back
OL,17,Finto stores.
